analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: Strategic Neutrality Amid Rising Fiscal Volatility. The GMS print of 52 confirms Phase 2 stagnation, where suppressed liquidity convexity and negative market breadth offset localized asset appreciation. While VIX compression suggests near-term stability, the widening of high-yield spreads and the geopolitical shock of global tariffs signal impending regime degradation. Stagnant real interest rates and flat inflation proxies necessitate a disciplined stance, eschewing risk expansion until clarity. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

reports.ID: Netralitas Strategis di Tengah Volatilitas Fiskal. Angka GMS 52 mengonfirmasi stagnasi Fase 2, di mana konveksitas likuiditas yang tertekan dan keluasan pasar negatif mengimbangi apresiasi aset lokal. Meskipun kompresi VIX menunjukkan stabilitas jangka pendek, pelebaran spread imbal hasil tinggi dan guncangan tarif global menandakan degradasi rezim. Suku bunga riil yang stagnan dan proksi inflasi yang datar mengharuskan sikap disiplin, menghindari ekspansi risiko hingga kejelasan tercapai. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
